UNRELEASED  ts-klassen  <qrpc@su-shiki.com>

	* VERSION: 0.2.1
	q_vvx_worker config is optional and defaults when missing.
	q_vvx_worker preloads additional GPU libraries from additional_libraries.
	q_vvx_worker logs model load errors with style id and model path.
	q_vvx_worker adds a --gpu flag to opt into GPU synthesis (CPU by default).
	q_vvx_worker adds subsystem config use_gpu to append --gpu to workers.


